sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Calendar Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open calendar page
    UI->>LW: mount()
    LW-->>UI: Initialize month/week/day state
    LW->>DB: Query calendar events for current range
    DB-->>LW: Events for student and modules
    LW-->>UI: Render calendar grid/list

    User->>UI: Change view (month/week/day)
    UI->>LW: setView(view, date)
    LW->>DB: Query events for selected range
    DB-->>LW: Filtered events
    LW-->>UI: Re-render selected view

    User->>UI: Navigate prev/next period
    UI->>LW: prevMonth/nextMonth (or week/day navigation)
    LW->>DB: Query events for new period
    DB-->>LW: Updated events
    LW-->>UI: Re-render calendar

    User->>UI: Click event
    UI->>LW: select event id
    LW-->>UI: Open event modal with details
